rows.label: qst001802_msg0001
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Fancy meeting you here!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0002
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]My Blade got lost, so I'm
waiting here for her.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0003
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Damn it! Olua sent you, didn't she?!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0004
rows.name: As you can see, I'm perfectly fine!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0005
rows.name: But I don't want to go back to Olua!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0006
rows.name:
She's always nagging me to "get
stronger!" She's so strict!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]Just now, a Moks Eluca blew me away
and I fell into the Cloud Sea...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0008
rows.name:
The fact that she sent you
here means she doesn't think
I can get back on my own.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0009
rows.name:
She talked me into this
training journey, but...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0010
rows.name:
I haven't grown at all, and
Olua doesn't trust me...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0011
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]That's why I'm quitting being a Driver!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0012
rows.name: Let's talk to Romney.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0013
rows.name: Ask if he can get back on his own.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0014
rows.name:
Tell him it's natural to be
inexperienced at his age.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0015
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]C-can I...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0016
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Of course not!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0017
rows.name:
Damn it! So I have to go
back to Olua after all.

rows.label: qst001802_msg0018
rows.name:
Ugh, what an annoying Blade! I have
to give her a piece of my mind!

rows.label: qst001802_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Well, I know I'm young, but...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0021
rows.name:
If I try my best, do you think
I can become an amazing Driver
like you guys someday?

rows.label: qst001802_msg0022
rows.name: I see...

rows.label: qst001802_msg0023
rows.name:
I guess I'll go back to Olua...
and give her a piece of my mind!
